                  "pageId": 1583856,
                  "revisionId": 2794101,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Bonus scales off of base health, i.e. before any mods or other health bonuses such as Arcane Blessing or Azure Archon Shard 's health bonus."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
